# Service Ownership Boundary

- **Loupe owns** PDF rendering and visual inspection UX.
- **Codex owns** extraction and normalized reusable intelligence.
- **Lint owns** policy/rules, reporting semantics, and workflow orchestration.
- Keep this repo UI-focused; do not embed extraction pipelines or policy engines here.
- For offshoots (Forge, Trap, Impose, Marks, etc.), assign each capability to one owner layer and integrate through contracts.
